[
  " Elisabeth (Liz) Mohn is the widow of Reinhard Mohn, whose family has run media conglomerate Bertelsmann for five generations.",
  "A former secretary at the company, she is now the vice chair of its board, and, with her three children, owns 19% of the firm.",
  "The other 81% is owned by the Bertelsmann Foundation, which is dedicated to education and fostering dialogue between different nations and cultures.",
  "Bertelsmann owns 75% of Penguin Random House, 75.1% of European entertainment network RTL Group and all of magazine publisher Gruner + Jahr."
]